These are Puzzles for 2x2 Level 6

.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-6-1::.
There are 2 different favourite colors: yellow, pink
The people's birthday is in 2 different months: october, december
1. the person who's birthday is in october is on the far left##1
2. the person who's birthday is in december is not the person who likes pink##6

.:: Answer ::.
|         |   1    |     2      |
| Food    | pink   | yellow  |
| Sport   | october | december |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-6-2::.
2 different brands of cigars are smoked: prince, vegafina
2 different games are played: backgammon, chess
1. the person playing backgammon is on the left of the person playing chess##1
2. the person playing backgammon is not the vegafina-smoker##6

.:: Answer ::.
|        |   1   |     2      |
| Food   | prince | vegafina      |
| Pet    | backgammon  | chess |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-6-3::.
House: modern, wooden
City: edinburgh, hamburg
1. the wooden house is on the left of the modern house##1
2. the person traveling to edinburgh is not the modern house##6

.:: Answer ::.
|         |    1     |    2    |
| Food    | wooden  | modern    |
| Sport   | edinburgh | hamburg |

